        <li><span class="vcp-chk" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>Gratis verzending vanaf €39</li>
        <li><span class="vcp-chk" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>30 dagen niet goed? Geld terug!</li>
        <li><span class="vcp-chk" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>Designed in the Netherlands</li>
      </ul>
      <div id="vcp-rating" aria-label="Beoordeling 9,4 uit 10">
