        <p id="vcp-s2-sub">Vul je e-mailadres in en ontvang jouw persoonlijke kortingscode.</p>
        <div id="vcp-timer">
          <span style="font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0" aria-hidden="true">⏱</span>
          <span class="vcp-timer-lbl">Aanbod verloopt over</span>
          <span id="vcp-timer-cnt" aria-live="polite">10:00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vcp-field">
